#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn45.11"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.11:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.11:0.2"
msgid "2. Vihāravagga "
msgstr "2. Meditation "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.11:0.3"
msgid "11. Paṭhamavihārasutta "
msgstr "11. Meditation (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn45.11:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.11:1.2"
msgid "“Icchāmahaṃ, bhikkhave, aḍḍhamāsaṃ paṭisallīyituṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I wish to go on retreat for a fortnight. "

msgctxt "sn45.11:1.3"
msgid "Namhi kenaci upasaṅkamitabbo, aññatra ekena piṇḍapātanīhārakenā”ti. "
msgstr "No-one should approach me, except for the one who brings my alms-food.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.11:1.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paṭissutvā nāssudha koci bhagavantaṃ upasaṅkamati, aññatra ekena piṇḍapātanīhārakena. "
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” replied those mendicants. And no-one approached him, except for the one who brought the alms-food. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.13, sc2
msgctxt "sn45.11:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassa aḍḍhamāsassa accayena paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then after a fortnight had passed, the Buddha came out of retreat and addressed the mendicants: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.11:2.2"
msgid "“yena svāhaṃ, bhikkhave, vihārena paṭhamābhisambuddho viharāmi, tassa padesena vihāsiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, I’ve been practicing part of the meditation I practiced when I was first awakened. "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.3"
msgid "So evaṃ pajānāmi: "
msgstr "I understand that "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.4"
msgid "‘micchādiṭṭhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "there’s feeling conditioned by wrong view "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.5"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ … pe … "
msgstr "and feeling conditioned by right view. … "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.6"
msgid "micchāsamādhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "There’s feeling conditioned by wrong immersion, "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.7"
msgid "sammāsamādhipaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "and feeling conditioned by right immersion. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.11:2.8"
msgid "chandapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "There’s feeling conditioned by desire, "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.9"
msgid "vitakkapaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "by thought, "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.10"
msgid "saññāpaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "and by perception. "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.11"
msgid "chando ca avūpasanto hoti, vitakko ca avūpasanto hoti, saññā ca avūpasantā hoti, tappaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "As long as desire, thought, and perception are not stilled, there is feeling conditioned by that. "

msgctxt "sn45.11:2.12"
msgid "chando ca vūpasanto hoti, vitakko ca vūpasanto hoti, saññā ca vūpasantā hoti, tappaccayāpi vedayitaṃ; "
msgstr "When desire, thought, and perception are stilled, there is feeling conditioned by that. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: āyāmaṃ → vāyāmo (bj) | vāyāmaṃ (s1-3)
msgctxt "sn45.11:2.13"
msgid "appattassa pattiyā atthi āyāmaṃ, tasmimpi ṭhāne anuppatte tappaccayāpi vedayitan’”ti. "
msgstr "There is effort to attain the unattained. When that state has been attained, there is also feeling conditioned by that.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.11:2.14"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

